item.title: Tech I use
item.description: This is the tech I am using, I’ll probably add more detail after time. And yes, I did name them all after my favourite Pokemon. Daily Drivers Mamoswine: Lenevo Thinkpad T470s (running Manjaro) - primary laptop Rotom: iPhone 13 Pro - phone Phantump: Airpod (Gen 2) - earbuds Wooper: iPad Air (Gen 2) - tablet
